com.bandyer.android_sdk.intent

Class BandyerIntent

  • com.bandyer.android_sdk.intent.BandyerIntent

  • public class BandyerIntent

    This custom Intent class is used to start a chat or a call in the Bandyer Environment and needs to be created with Builder class provided.
